Package magellan.library.utils.transformation

Interface ReportTransformer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoxTransformer, IdentityTransformer, MapTransformer, TwoLevelTransformer
    public interface ReportTransformer
    An interface for classes that transform coordinates. Possibly used by a report parser to translate a report.

      • getWrappers

        java.util.Collection<Region> getWrappers​(Region r,
                                         GameData data)
        Returns all wrapper regions for the data that "wrap to" r. I.e., if the region lies at the (right or left )edge of its box, this method returns wrappers to this region that are at an opposing edge and have the same ID as r.
        Returns:
        All wrapper regions to r
        See Also:
        GameData.wrappers(), MagellanFactory.createWrapper(CoordinateID, Region, GameData), Region.Visibility.WRAP
